# Authentication Routes

## Register User

```http
POST /api/auth/register
```

### Request Body

```json
{
  "fullName": "Leniency Yowika",
  "email": "lead@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}
```

---

## Login User

```http
POST /api/auth/login
```

### Request Body

```json
{
  "email": "lead@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}
```

---

## Get Current User

```http
GET /api/auth/me
```

---

# Vendor Routes

## Create Vendor

```http
POST /api/vendors
```

### Request Body

```json
{
  "businessName": "LeadTech Ltd",
  "businessEmail": "info@leadtech.com",
  "phoneNumber": "+2348012345678",
  "address": "Lagos, Nigeria",
  "cacNumber": "RC24689"
}
```

---

## Get All Vendors

```http
GET /api/vendors
```

### Search & Pagination

```http
GET /api/vendors?search=lead&page=1&limit=10
```

---

## Get Single Vendor

```http
GET /api/vendors/:id
```

---

## Update Vendor

```http
PATCH /api/vendors/:id
```

---

## Delete Vendor

```http
DELETE /api/vendors/:id
```

---

## Get Vendor Trust Score

```http
GET /api/vendors/:id/trust-score
```

This endpoint automatically:

* recalculates trust score
* updates vendor reputation
* emits webhook events
* triggers background jobs

